metadata.name: R1DER ON THE STORM
metadata.description:
We got inspiration from iconic Need for Speed Underground 2 soundtrack - Snoop Dogg feat. The Doors - Riders on the Storm. And tried to imagine what such a rider would look like. Of course with some artistic assumptions.

— Model by Rodion Afonin (Outside.inc). CGI and post production Andrew Kuzmin (ko0oz).
— 35 million polygons
— 40gb of disk space
— 4666x8296
